   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Rehabilitation center for 60 disabled in Poland</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">At the Pay it Forward Foundation we believe people, who get in a wheelchair as a result of an accident can live independently. We can&apos;t let sorrow, loneliness and helplessness ruin their lives.It is important to provide rehabilitation and therapy ASAP. That&apos;s why we are creating Janaszkowo Settlement in Poland. The rehabilitation center will be situated in the underground. We still need furniture and special equipment to provide regular, specialized treatments for over 60 disabled people a year.</narrative>
  </description>
